title: I have a code for a free ''Dreadknight Garen'' Skin
body: And I am unable to redeem it, everytime I try I get the same error message. ''There was a problem fulfilling your store items, please try again'' is it just not available right now or is the even over? it says the code expires in 04-05-2018. Please help, Ive been playing garen and i have lv4 on him and i want this skin :)

replies.body: Sorry for the delay, the mighty juggernaut has been added to your account now.  :D
